===Pronunciation===
[[Category:Hebrew language]]
שׁמרון / shômerôn / sho-mer-one'

===Etymology===
From the active participle of [[שׁמר]] {{HH|8104}}; watch station; 

===Proper noun===
'''שׁמרון'''

# Shomeron, a place in Palestine: - [[Samaria]].

